{"tid":1089781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"見到曾經追過既女仔結婚","createTime":"2019-04-03T04:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T04:29:08.000Z","uid":190320,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ed0f626b7673152d78d690029eb80f29e698f6","tid":1089781,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"心入面己經一早放低左佢<br />\n諗起自己曾經鍾意過佢,追求過佢<br />\n曾經佢一舉手一投足都另我心情改變<br />\n到而家自己心如止水<br />\n覺得一齊既轉變都好神奇<br />\n有時覺得係廣闊宇宙中,人類幾千年歷史中,<br />\n能夠遇上佢,同佢四目交頭過己經賺左<br />\n知道佢只不過係我生命中既一個過客<br />\n衷心祝福佢呢一生都幸福快樂,平平安安<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065422c206811f7e4681a2a915770da397e8e671","tid":1089781,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:24:39.000Z","msg":"又叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e22fbe7bcb450ebdcd5cfd9729e80b9c43ea615","tid":1089781,"uid":124277,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"有無唸過茫茫人海中<br />\n你同隔離屋個阿嬸都四目交投過"},{"pid":"57593ab7ea3661c1d24fbbad61f64045ae9eb508","tid":1089781,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"065422c206811f7e4681a2a915770da397e8e671","tid":1089781,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:24:39.000Z","msg":"又叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:27:39.000Z","msg":"咁唔算叫春掛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d005f140eba3b60b0fb3f08ac1e41c448a1c47","tid":1089781,"uid":190320,"li